story.text: Went to Great Falls, then back. Horseback riding today. Still exhausted. I need a 12 hour night and it will not be happening anytime soon (maybe Sunday). I cannot remember the last time I was this tired. Perhaps last summer. Need to work on new shape for a solid day - but no days available.
